      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-4">
          How Our AI Song Generator Works
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--muted-foreground)] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Creating a personalized song with AI is simple. No musical experience required—just your story and 2 minutes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {steps.map((step) => (
          <div class="relative p-6 bg-[var(--card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] hover:border-[var(--primary)]/50 transition-all">
            <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--primary)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg">
              {step.number}
            </div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[var(--primary)]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <Icon name={step.icon} class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--primary)]" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-2">{step.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--muted-foreground)] text-sm">{step.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-10">
        <a
          href="/create"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[var(--primary)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]/90 text-white font-medium px-6 h-12 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-[var(--primary)]/25 hover:shadow-[var(--primary)]/40 transition-all"
        >
          Start Creating Now
          <Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AI Technology Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-6">
            Why AI-Generated Songs Sound This Good
          </h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
            <p>
              Our AI song generator represents the cutting edge of music technology. Using advanced machine learning models trained on millions of songs, our AI understands the nuances of melody, harmony, rhythm, and lyrics that make music emotionally powerful.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              When you use our AI music generator, you're not getting a simple text-to-speech output or a generic template. The AI analyzes your story, identifies emotional themes, and crafts original lyrics that capture the essence of what you want to express. It then composes a unique melody and produces a full instrumental arrangement in your chosen genre.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              The result? A professionally produced song that sounds like it was created by a team of songwriters, composers, and producers—but delivered in 2 minutes instead of 2 weeks, at a fraction of the cost.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)] pt-4">AI Song Generator vs. Traditional Custom Songs</h3>
            
            <p>
              Traditional custom song services like <a href="/vs-songfinch" class="text-[var(--primary)] hover:underline">SongFinch</a> connect you with human songwriters. While talented, they typically charge $200-$500 and take 1-2 weeks to deliver. Our AI song maker creates comparable quality instantly for just $19.99.
            </p>

            <p>
              The AI doesn't get tired, doesn't have creative blocks, and delivers consistent quality every time. Plus, you can regenerate your song with different styles or details until it's perfect—something impossible with traditional services.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)] pt-4">Make a Song with AI: The Technology Behind the Magic</h3>
            
            <p>
              When you make a song with AI using YourBanger, you're leveraging the same type of neural network technology that powers the most advanced AI systems in the world. Our AI song maker has been trained on diverse musical styles, from classic rock and country to modern pop and hip-hop. This training allows it to understand what makes each genre unique—the chord progressions, rhythmic patterns, vocal styles, and production techniques that define different types of music.
            </p>

            <p>
              The AI music generator doesn't just string words together randomly. It understands narrative structure, emotional arcs, and how to craft lyrics that tell a compelling story. When you share details about a person or occasion, the AI identifies the most meaningful elements and weaves them into verses, choruses, and bridges that flow naturally and resonate emotionally.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="p-6 bg-[var(--card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)]">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--primary)]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="tabler:brain" class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--primary)]" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)]">Advanced AI Composition</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
              Our AI understands music theory, genre conventions, and emotional expression to create songs that feel authentic and professionally crafted.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 bg-[var(--card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)]">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--primary)]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="tabler:microphone-2" class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--primary)]" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)]">Professional AI Vocals</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
              Natural-sounding vocals with proper pitch, timing, and emotional delivery. Choose from multiple voice styles to match your song's mood.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 bg-[var(--card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)]">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--primary)]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="tabler:wave-sine" class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--primary)]" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)]">Studio-Quality Production</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
              Full instrumental arrangements with proper mixing and mastering. Your AI-generated song sounds ready for radio play.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[var(--secondary)]/30">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-4">
          What Will You Create?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--muted-foreground)] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Our AI song generator creates personalized songs for every occasion. Choose your moment and make it unforgettable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {useCases.map((useCase) => (
          <a 
            href={useCase.href}
            class="group relative p-6 bg-[var(--card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] hover:border-[var(--primary)]/50 transition-all overflow-hidden"
          >
            <div class={`absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br ${useCase.gradient} opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-5 transition-opacity`}></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[var(--primary)]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-[var(--primary)]/20 transition-colors">
                <Icon name={useCase.icon} class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--primary)]" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-2 group-hover:text-[var(--primary)] transition-colors">
                {useCase.title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">{useCase.description}</p>
              <div class="mt-4 flex items-center text-[var(--primary)] text-sm font-medium">
